   SOTG

   The Space Object Technology Group (SOTG) work was completed with the
   delivery of a draft proposed architecture in December, 1999.  The draft
   architecture can be accessed via this site.


   SSGSWG

   The Space, Satellite and Ground System Working Group (SSGSWG) was
   formed as working group of the Object Management Group (OMG) to
   continue the work of the SOTG and advance to the next stage, the
   development of software components.


